Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想加社團的時候 想學東西的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想挑戰名校的入學考試的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全都在事到臨頭前退怯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦嘗試沒有做過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總會想不順利的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不想要失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會不會後悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:07:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每到最後關頭總會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得這也不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:17.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\1c&H242D2B&\t(0,5780,0\fs40)\frz346.2\move(596,274,596,270,0,5754)}門禁前會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:17.73,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康粗圓體\bord0\1c&H353939&\t(0,5780,0\fs40)\frz344.3\move(70,388,44,384,0,5754)}我做了常吃的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最討厭自己這一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次要不要一起出去玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 你東西掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的 總共多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}數了一下 正好100萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你拿來幹嘛 要送去警局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家嚇到忘記了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真會找藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啦 我認真的 真的是嚇呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且掉了這個信封的人 好像是穿我們學校的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幾年級的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是瞄到她的背影一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}髮型和那邊那位很像 大概是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}味道很香 潤絲的香味？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這點線索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 頭髮那麼長的人大概不多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去看看一年級的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靜不下心來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬元…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}100萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 其實昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 我沒騙你 真的是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寫這本書的人是我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前是南極觀測員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我上國中的時候 她突然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後沒找到人 基本上也沒什麼遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我想去找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南極嗎？你能去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家也是這種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外婆 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師 學長 還有鄰居
